channel.title: "no response from server
channel.description:
I made a on RSPS and I tried to get on it after changing the IP in Gui.java and Client.java
I tried to connect to my server on the and it said "No response from server. Please try using a different world."
I used my no-ip as the IP for the and saw a few threads about this problem and I had my friends test it out and it said the same thing for them.
I have uTorrent and No-Ip running and full functioning, all ports forwarded, and the status checker on google says my server is online; the same with RSPS
My friends can't connect, I can't connect. What am I doing wrong?? Everything is working according to the server checkers and port forward checkers.
This is so frustrating!!
